name: Aurra Sing
Lore: 'Bounty hunter. Former student of the Force. After failing her Jedi training, Aurra became known for hunting down and killing Jedi Knights.',
Text: 'May use any ''stolen'' lightsaber. Once per turn, may steal a lightsaber from an opponent''s character just lost where present. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 while armed with a lightsaber).',
